The European Investment Bank (EIB) approved a EUR 300 million framework for financing transport and environmental projects in 2006 with grants from the Cohesion Fund. e EUR 100 million loan agreement was signed earlier, with the current agreement dealing with the use of the EUR 200 million provided.
